@startuml
!theme plain
skinparam sequenceArrowThickness 2
skinparam roundcorner 20
skinparam maxmessagesize 60

title Browse Public Site Sequence
participant Guest
participant HomePage
participant BlogAPI
participant PodcastAPI
participant prisma
participant BlogPost
participant Podcast

Guest -> HomePage: Navigate to homepage
HomePage -> BlogAPI: GET /api/blog
BlogAPI -> prisma: blogPost.findMany()
prisma -> BlogPost: query recent posts
BlogPost --> prisma: blog data
prisma --> BlogAPI: posts array
BlogAPI --> HomePage: recent blog posts

HomePage -> PodcastAPI: GET /api/podcast
PodcastAPI -> prisma: podcast.findMany()
prisma -> Podcast: query recent podcasts
Podcast --> prisma: podcast data
prisma --> PodcastAPI: podcasts array
PodcastAPI --> HomePage: recent podcasts

HomePage --> Guest: Display homepage with content

@enduml
